      • setFilterAction

        public PortMirroringFilter.Builder setFilterAction(java.lang.String filterAction)
        Possible values are:
        • PortMirroringFilter.FILTER_ACTION_MIRROR
        • PortMirroringFilter.FILTER_ACTION_DO_NOT_MIRROR
        If set to MIRROR, packets will be mirrored. If set to DO_NOT_MIRROR, packets will not be mirrored.
